<descript>
<abstract>Montserrat, 1983 is a scanned map of the British Overseas Territory Montserrat at a scale of 25,000. The map is georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. The original scanned file with additional information is also provided.</abstract>
<purpose>Scanned maps may be used for a variety of purposes. This image may be used in a GIS.</purpose>
</descript>
